wt.iba.value.service

Class IBAValueManagerEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • wt.events.KeyedEvent
      • wt.iba.value.service.IBAValueManagerEvent

  • public class IBAValueManagerEvent
extends KeyedEvent
    Used to represent events occurring within the iba service.

    The POST_COPY_ALL_IBAS is fired when the all the IBAs are copied for the links processed by the COPY_LINK event.The event target contains the collection of new links to which iba attributes are copied over.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
